---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Service — AmbitiousOS"
  description="Terms of service for AmbitiousOS and the Reading Ambitiously newsletter."
>
  <main class="section-padding">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose-custom">
      <nav class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-8">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-text-primary transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span class="mx-2">/</span>
        <span class="text-text-secondary">Terms</span>
      </nav>

      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <h2>Agreement</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing or using AmbitiousOS (&ldquo;the Service&rdquo;), operated by Reading Ambitiously,
        you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, do not use the Service.
      </p>

      <h2>The Service</h2>
      <p>
        AmbitiousOS provides AI-powered research and analysis tools, including an AI chat assistant,
        interactive knowledge graph, and curated content library. The Service is currently in private beta.
      </p>

      <h2>Access</h2>
      <p>
        Access to AmbitiousOS is granted on a per-user basis. You may not share your account credentials
        or provide access to unauthorized users. We reserve the right to revoke access at any time.
      </p>

      <h2>Content</h2>
      <p>
        All content within AmbitiousOS, including curated research, AI-generated responses, and the
        knowledge graph, is provided for informational purposes only. It does not constitute professional
        advice. The content is the intellectual property of Reading Ambitiously.
      </p>

      <h2>AI-Generated Content</h2>
      <p>
        AI chat responses are generated based on curated source material but may contain inaccuracies.
        You should independently verify any information before relying on it for important decisions.
      </p>

      <h2>Acceptable Use</h2>
      <p>You agree not to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the Service for any illegal purpose</li>
        <li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to the Service or its systems</li>
        <li>Scrape, copy, or redistribute content from the Service</li>
        <li>Use the Service to generate spam or misleading content</li>
        <li>Interfere with the Service's operation or other users' access</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        The Service is provided &ldquo;as is&rdquo; without warranties of any kind.
        We do not guarantee uninterrupted access, accuracy of content, or fitness for any particular purpose.
      </p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, Reading Ambitiously shall not be liable for any indirect,
        incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Service.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We may update these Terms at any time. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes
        acceptance of the updated Terms.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these Terms? Contact us at <a href="mailto:jack@readingambitiously.com">jack@readingambitiously.com</a>.</p>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>

<style>
  .prose-custom h1 { @apply text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-6; }
  .prose-custom h2 { @apply text-xl font-semibold text-text-primary mt-10 mb-3; }
  .prose-custom p { @apply text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4; }
  .prose-custom ul { @apply text-text-secondary leading-relaxed mb-4 pl-6 list-disc space-y-1; }
  .prose-custom a { @apply text-galaxy-sage hover:underline; }
</style>
